    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka: Student activists held under PTA moved to Tangalle Detention Center",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Convener of the Inter University Students' Federation Wasantha Mudalige, Hashantha Gunathilake, and Ven. Galwewa Siridhamma Thero, who are held under the Prevention of Terrorism Act for 90-days were moved to the Tangalle Central Detention Center.",
        "Police Spokesperson Att.-at-Law SSP Nihal Thalduwa said the Criminal Investigation Department and the Terrorism Investigation Division are conducting investigations on an possible link to an Anti-government Conspiracy.",
        "Minister of Defence, President Ranil Wickremesinghe on Monday (22) approved to detain and interrogate Wasantha Mudalige, Hashantha Gunathilake, and Ven. Galwewa Siridhamma Thero for a period of 90-days under the PTA.",
        "Sri Lanka: Student activists held under PTA moved to Tangalle Detention Center",
        "Man remanded for stealing liquor bottle from President\u2019s private residence"
